      <p>Not one mention anywhere of the disgusting habit of calculating or charging tip ...ON THE TAX! Yes, restaurants now present the bill total without telling you how much of the bill is tax (here in Houston, 8.25%) and then pre-calculate 20% tip on the total with the tax included (some require you pay the tip regardless of the actual quality of the service).</p>
